ids_alerts.rule_msg: INDICATOR-SHELLCODE x86 NOOP
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert ip $EXTERNAL_NET any -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"INDICATOR-SHELLCODE x86 NOOP"; content:"|90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90|",fast_pattern,nocase; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop,ruleset community; classtype:shellcode-detect; sid:648; rev:18; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS Query to a *.abuser .eu Domain
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS Query to a *.abuser .eu Domain"; dns.query; content:".abuser.eu"; fast_pattern; nocase; endswith; reference:url,freedns.afraid.org/domain/registry/; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2040018; rev:2; metadata:attack_target Client_and_Server, created_at 2022_11_28, deployment Perimeter, performance_impact Low, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2023_03_02, mitre_tactic_id TA0011, mitre_tactic_name Command_And_Control, mitre_technique_id T1568, mitre_technique_name Dynamic_Resolution;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS HTTP Request to a *.abuser .eu Domain
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET INFO DYNAMIC_DNS HTTP Request to a *.abuser .eu Domain"; flow:established,to_server; http.host; content:".abuser.eu"; endswith; reference:url,freedns.afraid.org/domain/registry/; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2040019; rev:2; metadata:attack_target Client_and_Server, created_at 2022_11_28, deployment Perimeter, performance_impact Low, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2023_03_02, mitre_tactic_id TA0011, mitre_tactic_name Command_And_Control, mitre_technique_id T1568, mitre_technique_name Dynamic_Resolution;)
